Suggests:
 fieldworks
Description: A suite of programs to manage language and cultural data - applications
 FieldWorks is a suite of software tools to help language development teams
 manage language and cultural data, with support for complex scripts.
 .
 This required package contains the applications.
 .
 For further information, please visit http://fieldworks.sil.org/

Package: fieldworks
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 fieldworks-applications (>= ${binary:Version})
Description: A suite of programs to manage language and cultural data
 FieldWorks is a suite of software tools to help language development teams
 manage language and cultural data, with support for complex scripts.
 .
 This is a metapackage that installs both the required and the optional
 parts of FieldWorks.
 .
 For further information, please visit http://fieldworks.sil.org/

